## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and reports, which may not capture the full scope of the issue across different regions and healthcare settings. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of the pandemic and its impact on the healthcare industry means that new factors may emerge that influence worker retention. The data is also limited to the sources accessed and may not include all perspectives or recent developments in the field.